#: ../../migration.rst:146 9d7f3fbe35a1484484b99c6cb829680e
msgid ""
"Please note that NethSecurity web server only listens on HTTPS (port 443) "
"for reverse proxy rules. If you had any reverse proxy rules configured on "
"NethServer 7 using HTTP (port 80), you will need to update them to use "
"HTTPS. See the :ref:`reverse proxy documentation <reverse_proxy-http-"
"section>` for more details."
msgstr ""
